2K-Teint SARL,MohammedKermoudi, Khalid Kermoudi, Laila Kermoudi, Mounia Kermoudi, Salma Kermoudi in Rabia Kermoudi nosijo svoje stroške in stroške, ki sta jih priglasila Komisija in Evropska investicijska banka.

eur-lex.europa.eu

2K-Teint SARL, Mohammed Kermoudi, Khalid Kermoudi, Laila Kermoudi, Mounia Kermoudi, Salma Kermoudi and Rabia Kermoudi are ordered to pay, in addition to their own costs, the costs incurred by the Commission and the European Investment Bank (EIB).

eur-lex.europa.eu

Faizullah Noorzai AkhtarMohammedMira Khan je pomemben talibanski finančnik, pri katerem so svoja sredstva investirali visoki talibanski voditelji.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Faizullah Noorzai Akhtar Mohammed Mira Khan has served as a prominent Taliban financier with whom senior Taliban leaders invested funds.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Abdul Kabir Mohammad Jan je bil član talibanskega vodstvenega sveta na visoki ravni, kar je sporočilMohammedOmar oktobra 2006, in je bil imenovan za vojaškega poveljnika vzhodnega območja oktobra 2007.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Abdul Kabir Mohammad Jan was a member of the Taliban’s high leadership council as announced by Mohammed Omar in October 2006, and was appointed military commander of the eastern zone in Oct 2007.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Vnos „Jaish-I-Momhammed (tudi Army ofMohammed),Pakistan“ pod naslovom „Pravne osebe, skupine in subjekti“ se nadomesti z naslednjim

eur-lex.europa.eu

The entry ‘Jaish-I-Momhammed (aka Army of Mohammed), Pakistan’ under the heading ‘Legal persons, groups and entities’ shall be replaced by the following

eur-lex.europa.eu

SayyedMohammedHaqqani je povezan z Gulbbudinom Hekmatyarjem in je dolgotrajen pristaš mule Mohammeda Omarja.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Sayyed Mohammed Haqqani is allied with Gulbbudin Hekmatyar and has been a long-standing supporter of Mullah Mohammed Omar.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Drugi podatki: (a) sedež v Pakistanu, (b) operacije v Afganistanu: Herat, Džalalabad, Kabul, Kandahar, Mazar, Šarif, tudi operacije na Kosovu in v Čečeniji, (c) do 21. 10. 2008 je seznam ZN vključeval vnosa ‚Al Rashid Trust‘ (vključen v seznam 6. 10. 2001) in ‚Aid Organization of the Ulema, Pakistan‘ (vključen v seznam 24. 4. 2002 in spremenjen 25. 7. 2006); navedena vnosa sta bila 21. oktobra 2008 združena v ta vnos, (d) kartel je ustanovil Mufti Rashid Ahmad Ledahyanoy, (e) povezan s skupino Jaish-i-Mohammed,(f) v Pakistanu prepovedan od oktobra 2001, (g) kljub zaprtju pisarn v Pakistanu februarja 2007 je kartel nadaljeval s svojimi dejavnostmi.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Other information: (a) Headquarters in Pakistan; (b) Operations in Afganistan: Herat, Jalalabad, Kabul, Kandahar, Mazar, Sherif, also operations in Kosovo, Chechnya; (c) Until 21.10.2008 the UN list included the entries “Al Rashid Trust” (listed on 6.10.2001) and “Aid Organization of the Ulema, Pakistan” (listed on 24.4.2002 and amended on 25.7.2006); The two entries were consolidated into this entity on 21 October 2008; (d) Founded by Mufti Rashid Ahmad Ledahyanoy; (e) Associated with Jaish-i-Mohammed, (f) Banned in Pakistan since October 2001; (g) Despite the closure of its offices in Pakistan in February 2007 it has continued its activities.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Povezan s člani LIFG v Združenem kraljestvu, vključnozMohammedomBenhammedijem in Ismailom Kamoko, vodilnim članom LIFG v Združenem kraljestvu, ki je bil junija 2007 v Združenem kraljestvu obsojen zaradi financiranja terorizma.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Associated with members of the LIFG in the United Kingdom, including Mohammed Benhammedi and Ismail Kamoka, a senior member of the LIFG in the United Kingdom who has been convicted and sentenced in the United Kingdom in June 2007 based on charges of terrorist funding.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Jalaluddin Haqqani je v tesnih odnosih z Osamo bin Ladnom inMohammedomOmarjem.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Jalaluddin Haqqani has close relations with Usama bin Laden and Mohammed Omar.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Drugi podatki: (a) član talibanskega sveta, ki usklajuje pobiranje zakata (islamskega davka) iz province Balučistan v Pakistanu, (b) vodja talibanske finančne komisije, (c) povezan z MullahomMohammedomOmarjem, (d) glavni finančni sodelavec Omarja in eden njegovih najbližjih svetovalcev, (e) pripadnik plemena Ishaqzai.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Other information: (a) Member of a Taliban Council that coordinates the collection of zakat (Islamic tax) from Baluchistan Province, Pakistan, (b) Head of Taliban Financial Commission, (c) Associated with Mullah Mohammed Omar, (d) Served as Omar’s principal finance officer and one of his closest advisors, (e) Belongs to Ishaqzai tribe.

eur-lex.europa.eu

G. ker po navedbah organizacij za varstvo človekovih pravic trenutno v zaporih pridržanih veliko število spletnih oporečnikov – največ od tega na Kitajskem – vključno s Haom Wujem, kitajskim avtorjem spletnih dnevnikov in snemalcem dokumentarcev, Yang Zilijem, kitajskim spletnim oporečnikom, Motdžabo Saminedžadom, iranskim avtorjem spletnih dnevnikov,MohammedomAbujem, tunizijskim odvetnikom, Pham Hong Sonom, vietnamskim zdravnikom, in Habibom Salehom, sirijskim spletnim novinarjem; ker najnovejši primeri zadevajo egiptovska avtorja spletnih dnevnikov Mohameda Šarkavija in Karima El Šerja

europarl.europa.eu

G. whereas, according to human rights organisations, a large number of cyber-dissidents are detained in prison - most of them in China - including Hao Wu, Chinese blogger and documentary filmmaker, Yang Zili, Chinese cyber-dissident, Shi Tao, Chinese journalist at the daily Dangdai Shangbao, Motjaba Saminejad, Iranian blogger, Mohammed Abbou, Tunisian lawyer, Pham Hong Son, Vietnamese doctor and Habib Saleh, Syrian online journalist; whereas the most recent cases concern the Egyptian bloggers Mohamed Sharkawy and Karim Lel-shaer

europarl.europa.eu

Drugi podatki: (a) talibanski zbiralec sredstev, ki pogosto potuje v Zalivske države, (b) leta 2011 član finančne komisije talibanskega vrhovnega sveta, (c) njegova družina je ženitno povezana z MullahomMohammedomOmarjem, (d) domnevno se zadržuje na mejnem območju med Afganistanom in Pakistanom, (e) pripadnik etnične skupine Sadat.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Other information: (a) He is a Taliban fundraiser who frequently travels to Gulf States, (b) Member of Financial Commission of the Taliban Supreme Council as at 2011, (c) His family is linked by marriage to Mullah Mohammed Omar, (d) Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area, (e) Belongs to Sadat ethnic group.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Zaradi tesnih odnosov z Bacharjem al-Asadom inMohammedomNassifom Kheirom Bekom je vpleten v represivno politiko režima zoper nasprotnike.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Samir Joumaa's closeness to Bashar al-Assad and Mohammed Nassif Kheir Bek means that he is implicated in the policy of repression conducted by the regime against its opponents.

eur-lex.europa.eu

Svet je pozdravil miren potek predsedniških volitev v Egiptu inMohammeduMorsiju čestital ob izvolitvi za predsednika.

europa.eu

The Council welcomed the peaceful conduct of the presidential elections in Egypt and congratulated Mohammed Morsi on his election as President.
